reviews: Exactly what I needed for my bathroom barn door. Arrived on time.
Use it everyday. Gets nice and hot. Slim design is easy to hold, especially when doing your own hair. Arrived on time.
Son was super happy with his purchase. Has worn it everyday since. Arrived on time.
A little smaller than measurements used when ordering. Nice looking.
Daughter was super happy with the skateboard. Exactly what she thought it would be. Arrived early.
Nice looking container. Exactly what I thought it would be. Arrived on time.
The tablet works fine, etc., but I am quite dissapointed that the features I thought I'd be getting are not available to me as I am Canadian.

Bought this item online as a Christmas present for my daughter. The area that the tablet fits into is too big, so the tablet slides around in the case. You also have to take the tablet out of the case to charge it, etc., as there are no holes to allow you to plug in the tablet while in the case and because it slips around, it makes it difficult to use the holes provided for power button and volume. Pretty dissapointed :(
